data.description: Gulf Access Pool Home! TURNKEY Immaculate condition & updated! great location! 25 minutes to the river! assumable flood $ 600 annual, this home offers New 165mph rated Roof 2023, New A/C 2022, New pool heater 2023, pool resurfaced 2018, re screened 2023, New washer & dryer 2023, double door entry with vaulted ceilings, tiled floors main area of home, living room dining area combo, master bedroom offers tray ceiling, sliders to the lanai & two walk in closets, main bath includes a double sink high-top vanity, large custom tiled walk in shower & a private lavatory, there are two additional nicely appointed quest bedrooms with a hall bath on the other side of the home, the beautiful inviting family room / Kitchen is the place where you will want to entertain that offers an amazing water view, kitchen has a large granite breakfast bar with newer appliances, recessed lighting pantry & sliders out to your private tropical screened heated pool / spa oasis with lush plants & a beautiful upscaled landscape package, the extended concrete patio area offers a tranquil water fall station with exterior surround sound stereo, there is a 10k canopy boat lift with new composite decking a must see!
